{"type": "article", "id": 10159, "title": "「 儿童节可以准备起来了」之 Liaison桌子​", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-29T07:20:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141224wiNlDpYES3RrCMo6.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t米兰设计师 Daniele Ragazzo 设计了一款叫做 <span style=\"white-space:normal;\">“Liaison” 的桌子</span>，桌面是一块普通的玻璃，而桌腿则是不锈钢细管搭配彩色小球，看起来就像一个个彩色的棒棒糖。其灵感来源自设计师常常使用的大头针，营造出轻松活泼的装饰效果。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061412222DZfJHdbPiFC46Q5.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061412226Kgjtfaq9QRJU1op.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141223dmBX1i3Z5p2WfscV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.38247863\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141223V1COFJUMb7YmpI0N.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.99786325\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}